name: Shapes
description:
▪️ Use mouse scroll wheel to increase or decrease the speed
▪️ Use the 1 key to randomize the edge effect
▪️ Use the keys 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, and 7 to toggle effects
▪️ Use the 8 key to randomize the shape
▪️ Use the 9 key to capture a screenshot with the current width and height
